y'' + \frac {a^{2}b^{2}}{a^{2}\cos^{2}x} + b^{2}\sin^{2}(x) y'=0
  w = \frac{dy}{dx} \Rightarrow w' + \frac{a^2 b^2}{a^2\cos^2 x } + b^2\sin^2(x) w = 0 
 w' + b^2\sin^2(x)w = -\frac{a^2 b^2}{a^2\cos^2 x } = - \frac{b^2}{\cos^2 x} \quad a \neq 0
e^{b^2\int \sin^2(x) \ dx} = e^{b^2\int \frac{1}{2} \left( 1 - \cos 2x \right) \ dx} 
 =   e^{\frac{b^2}{2} ( x - \frac{\sin 2x}{2} )}
 \left( e^{\frac{b^2}{2} ( x - \frac{\sin 2x}{2} )} w \right)' = -e^{\frac{b^2}{2} ( x +- \frac{\sin 2x}{2} )}  \frac{b^2}{\cos^2 x}
 \therefore \   e^{\frac{b^2}{2} ( x - \frac{\sin 2x}{2} )} w = \int  -e^{\frac{b^2}{2} ( x - \frac{\sin 2x}{2} )}  \frac{b^2}{\cos^2x}  \ dx 
